Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫青野月音 15岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年春天 就会成为闪闪发光的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应如此 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,170)}{\1c&H8743E5&}{\3c&H0F0F0F&}{\fs60}{\i1}{\bord2}{\clip(0,0,1280,490)}新生活{\1c&H0DDDEE&}与{\1c&H8743E5&}吸血鬼
